# Gaudi Algorithm Overview

This page lists all Gaudi algorithms available in the Key4hep software stack,
collected from the active environment. Use the search box to filter by algorithm
name, package, or library. Click a package header to collapse or expand it; click
an algorithm name to reveal its properties.

Total: **{{ total_algorithms }} algorithms** across **{{ total_packages }} packages**.

```{raw} html
<style>
{% include "_overview_common.css.jinja2" %}
#algorithm-overview .alg-props-table td:nth-child(3) {
  max-width: 20em;
}
#algorithm-overview .alg-props-table td:nth-child(3) code {
  white-space: pre-wrap;
  word-break: break-word;
  overflow-wrap: break-word;
}
</style>

<div id="algorithm-overview">
  <div class="alg-filter-bar">
    <input type="text" id="alg-search" placeholder="Filter by name, package, or library…" autocomplete="off" />
    <span id="alg-stats">Showing {{ total_algorithms }} of {{ total_algorithms }} algorithms in {{ total_packages }} packages</span>
  </div>

  {%- for package, algorithms in packages.items() %}
  <div class="alg-package-group" data-package="{{ package | e }}">
    <div class="alg-package-header">
      <span class="alg-package-name">{{ (package if package else "(unknown)") | e }}</span>
      <span class="alg-package-meta">
        <span class="alg-package-count">{{ algorithms | length }} algorithm{%- if algorithms | length != 1 %}s{%- endif %}</span>
        <span class="alg-package-toggle">&#9660;</span>
      </span>
    </div>
    <div class="alg-cards-container">
      {%- for alg in algorithms %}
      <div class="alg-card" data-name="{{ alg.name | e }}" data-lib="{{ alg.lib | e }}" data-package="{{ package | e }}">
        <div class="alg-card-header">
          <span class="alg-name">{{ alg.name | e }}</span>
          <span class="alg-card-right">
            {%- if alg.lib %}
            <span class="alg-lib-badge">{{ alg.lib | e }}</span>
            {%- endif %}
            <span class="alg-card-toggle">&#9658;</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="alg-card-body">
          {%- if alg.description %}
          <p class="alg-description">{{ alg.description | e }}</p>
          {%- endif %}
          {%- if alg.properties %}
          <table class="alg-props-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Property</th>
                <th>Type</th>
                <th>Default</th>
                <th>Description</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              {%- for prop_name, prop_info in alg.properties.items() %}
              <tr>
                <td><code>{{ prop_name | e }}</code></td>
                <td><code>{{ prop_info.get("type", "") | e }}</code></td>
                <td>{{ prop_info.value | render_prop_value }}</td>
                <td>{{ prop_info.description | e }}</td>
              </tr>
              {%- endfor %}
            </tbody>
          </table>
          {%- else %}
          <em>No properties available.</em>
          {%- endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
  {%- endfor %}
</div>

<script>
{% include "_overview_common.js.jinja2" %}
</script>
```
